{"name":"Transfer Preparation","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You&rsquo;ve unlocked more potential for your prepared spells. You can spend 10 minutes consulting your spellbook to replace one spell you&rsquo;ve prepared with another spell of the same level that appears on all four spell lists.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_theurge"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-21T16:26:06.847-05:00","version":{"schema":0.769,"foundry":"10.288","system":"4.2.6"}}},"level":{"value":4},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666389831663,"modifiedTime":1666391305248,"lastModifiedBy":"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx"},"_id":"14A0CjuwfY7nDaDB","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3}}
{"name":"Exploitive Beacon","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your magical energy is unpredictable and sometimes has uncontrollable consequences. You gain the @Compendium[pf2e-novel-options-magic.novel-magic-spells.zK3kk2iy7yGlO8ph]{Exploitive Beacon}&nbsp;exploit spell. Increase the number of Focus Points in your focus pool by 1.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_theurge"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"add","path":"system.resources.focus.max","value":1}],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-21T16:26:06.847-05:00","version":{"schema":0.769,"foundry":"10.288","system":"4.2.6"}}},"level":{"value":10},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666390432115,"modifiedTime":1666391305249,"lastModifiedBy":"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx"},"_id":"1EkrhPIklcbKTeXt","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3}}
{"name":"Blessed Presence","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Your deity has permanently blessed you and you revel in the attention. You are permanently under the effects of a @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.XSujb7EsSwKl19Uu]{Bless} spell. The level of this spell is equal to the highest level spell slot you can cast. The emanation of this spell drops to 5ft at the end of any turn in which you didn&rsquo;t spend an action concentrating on the spell.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["divine","enchantment","mental","hb_zealot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-20T12:59:34.557-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"level":{"value":16},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.vEV6kCryPaiGzpOI"}},"_id":"1n8pcBkgVoJ9cnCf"}
{"_id":"1pUOJW5c8nsMKTeA","name":"Attack of Opportunity","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature within your reach uses a manipulate action or a move action, makes a ranged attack, or leaves a square during a move action it's using.</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You swat a foe that leaves an opening. Make a melee Strike against the triggering creature. If your attack is a critical hit and the trigger was a manipulate action, you disrupt that action. This Strike doesn't count toward your multiple attack penalty, and your multiple attack penalty doesn't apply to this Strike.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_zealot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":"attack-of-opportunity","schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"reaction"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.NMWXHGWUcZGoLDKb"}}}
{"name":"Call Spellbook","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","effects":[],"flags":{},"system":{"description":{"value":"<p>You're mystically connected to any spellbook that bears your sigil and can call it to your hand. Choose one of your spellbooks that you have cast @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.AUctDF2fqPZN2w4W]{Sigil} on, you teleport it into your hand from up to 1 mile away.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_theurge"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.794,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-10-21T16:26:06.847-05:00","version":{"schema":0.769,"foundry":"10.288","system":"4.2.6"}}},"level":{"value":4},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"action"},"actionCategory":{"value":"interaction"},"actions":{"value":1},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.2.6","coreVersion":"10.288","createdTime":1666389548475,"modifiedTime":1666391305247,"lastModifiedBy":"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx"},"_id":"39HO5ILREryxcNsU","folder":null,"sort":0,"ownership":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3}}
{"name":"Versatile Divine Force","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You can channel the entire realm of possibilities of your divine magic into yourself. Once during your daily preparations, you can use a spell slot to hold that infinite potential, rather than using it to prepare a spell. When you use @Compendium[pf2e-novel-options-magic.novel-magic-actions.W2XgBLycybWegHqQ]{Divine Force}, you can expend this special spell slot to immediately prepare and cast a spell that you have access to at 2 levels lower than the slot's level. (As normal for preparing spells, you can use a spell of an even-lower level, heightening it accordingly.) You don't have any spell prepared in that slot until you cast from that slot.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_zealot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-20T12:59:34.557-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"level":{"value":18},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.E9CQDdafVFRkanl8"}},"_id":"6jzjrA1nIRPAuZvE"}
{"name":"Judgement of Wrath","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You&rsquo;ve learned to call on the protective powers of your faith. You gain the @Compendium[pf2e-novel-options-magic.novel-magic-spells.zX0NN1D7K3yvdGUp]{Judgement of Wrath} judgement spell and a focus pool of 1 Focus Point. You refill your focus pool during your daily preparations, and you can regain 1 Focus Point by spending 10 minutes using the Refocus activity to pray to your deity or do service toward their causes.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_zealot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":{"datetime":"2022-08-20T12:59:34.557-05:00","version":{"schema":null,"foundry":"9.269","system":"3.13.5.16"}}},"level":{"value":6},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.8QcMXLl93k6zOMdF"}},"_id":"8WHtzzjtxLfWBPFk"}
{"name":"Deity's Domain","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>You embody an aspect of your deity. Choose one of your deity's domains. You gain the domain's initial domain spell as a devotion spell.</p>\n<p>It costs 1 Focus Point to cast a focus spell, and you start with a focus pool of 1 Focus Point. You refill your focus pool during your daily preparations, and you can regain 1 Focus Point by spending 10 minutes using the Refocus activity to pray to your deity or do service toward their causes.</p>\n<p>Focus spells are automatically heightened to half your level rounded up. Focus spells don't require spell slots, nor can you cast them using spell slots. Certain feats can give you more focus spells and increase the size of your focus pool, though your focus pool can never hold more than 3 Focus Points.</p>\n<p><strong>Special </strong>You can select this feat multiple times, selecting a different domain each time and gaining its domain spell.&nbsp;</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_zealot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"choices":"data.data.details.deities.domains","key":"ChoiceSet","prompt":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Prompt.DeitysDomain"}],"slug":"deitys-domain","schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":1},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":null,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.FXKIALDXAzEBfj5A"}},"_id":"8l4Ac4MWlkufmCWd"}
{"_id":"8lD5qUqgetpihN9I","name":"Advanced Deity's Domain","type":"feat","img":"systems/pf2e/icons/features/feats/feats.webp","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>Through your conviction, you have glimpsed the deeper secrets of your deity's domain. You gain an advanced domain spell from the domain you chose with @Compendium[pf2e-novel-options-magic.novel-magic-feats.8l4Ac4MWlkufmCWd]{Deity's Domain}. You can cast that spell as a devotion spell. Increase the number of Focus Points in your focus pool by 1.</p>"},"source":{"value":"Novel Options: Magic"},"traits":{"value":["hb_zealot"],"rarity":"common","custom":""},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"add","path":"data.resources.focus.max","value":1}],"slug":"advanced-deitys-domain","schema":{"version":0.769,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":12},"featType":{"value":"class"},"onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actionCategory":{"value":""},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[{"value":"Deity's Domain"}]},"location":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"gKRAixZcnc2H4VRx":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.JHJBmiyILzWdFRJO"}}}
